'''賴義鍠'''（{{bd|1967年|4月24日|CatIdx=L賴}}）[[中國國民黨籍|中國國民黨籍]][[臺中市|臺中市]]政治人物，現任[[臺中市議員|臺中市議員]]，曾任[[臺中縣議員|臺中縣議員]]。

==生平==
賴義鍠早在當兵時就曾加入[[中國國民黨|中國國民黨]]，後來離開[[藍營|藍營]]以[[無黨籍|無黨籍]]身分參選議員，標榜自己無黨無派，在沒有政黨奧援的情況下持續連任，經常在議事堂宣揚善念，著重於道德教育，地方風評與基層服務實力都受到肯定，成為[[藍營|藍]]、[[綠營|綠]]陣營拉攏對象<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/micro-reading/tw/2011-12-29/content_4819042.html | title = 2012選舉藍綠四位主將副手都到台中市爭取支持 | publisher = [[中國日報|中國日報]] | date = 2015-07-17 | language = zh-hans | access-date = 2017-08-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170807152022/http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/micro-reading/tw/2011-12-29/content_4819042.html | archive-date = 2017-08-07 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

2015年，[[中國國民黨|中國國民黨]]徵召原屬[[無黨籍|無黨籍]]的[[臺中市議員|臺中市議員]]賴義鍠參選[[立委|立委]]<ref>{{cite news | author = 洪敬浤 | url = https://video.udn.com/news/344378 | title = 迎戰何欣純 國民黨提名市議員賴義鍠 | publisher = [[聯合報|聯合報]] | date = 2015-07-17 | language = zh-TW | accessdate = 2017-08-06 | archive-date = 2017-08-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170806143851/https://video.udn.com/news/344378 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，最終在黨內高層親自勸說下，才同意披藍袍參選立委，依照規定入黨接受徵召<ref>{{cite news | author = 施曉光 | url = http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/1382726 | title = 「情蒐風波」當事人 賴義鍠獲國民黨徵召挑戰何欣純 | publisher = [[自由時報|自由時報]] | date = 2015-07-17 | language = zh-TW | accessdate = 2017-08-06 | archive-date = 2018-12-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181203232024/http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/1382726 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=盧金足|url=http://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20150718000572-260107|title=國民黨徵召賴義鍠 迎戰何欣純|publisher=[[中時電子報|中時電子報]]|date=2015-07-18|language=zh-TW|accessdate=2015-08-22|archive-date=2017-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170806180425/http://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20150718000572-260107|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=蘇萱|url=https://www.nownews.com/news/20150924/1824058|title=何欣純清新拚連任　賴義鍠披藍袍搶攻|publisher=[[NOWnews|NOWnews]]|date=2015-09-24|language=zh-TW|accessdate=2017-08-06|archive-date=2017-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170806141201/https://www.nownews.com/news/20150924/1824058|dead-url=no}}</ref>，仍不敵綠營[[何欣純|何欣純]]，以大幅差距落敗<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.ettoday.net/news/20160117/632360.htm?t=%E4%B8%AD%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%83%E9%81%B8%E5%8D%80%EF%BC%8F%E8%B3%B4%E7%BE%A9%E9%8D%A0%E4%B8%8D%E6%95%B5%E7%B6%A0%E8%89%B2%E7%A5%A8%E5%80%89%E3%80%80%E4%BD%95%E6%AC%A3%E7%B4%94%E5%A4%A7%E5%8B%9D52917%E7%A5%A8 | title = 賴義鍠不敵綠色票倉　何欣純大勝52917票 | publisher = [[ETtoday|ETtoday]] | date = 2016-01-17 | language = zh-TW | accessdate = 2017-08-06 | archive-date = 2017-08-15 | archive-url = https://web